		"description": "<p>If you chose Path of the Revenant, you can strangle your foes at range with the sheer power of your hate. As an action, you may spend 4 exertion points to make a ranged spell attack against a creature you can see within 30 feet. It must make a Constitution save against your spell save DC or begin suffocating. The target may repeat this save at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success. The effect also ends if you are knocked unconscious or die or if the target has remove curse or similar magic cast on it. A creature that successfully saves against your Grasp of Vengeance is immune to it for 24 hours.</p>",
